int push(long x, int cap)
{	cap++;
	a[cap]=x;
	int ch=0;
	int loop=cap;
	while(ch==0&&loop!=1)
	{	if(x<a[loop/2])
		{	long temp = a[loop/2];
			a[loop/2]=x;
			a[loop]=temp;
			loop=loop/2;
		}
		else	
		{	ch=1;
		}
	}
	
}

	}
